.DT
add_vote
Disk World creator help
add_vote

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_vote -  This function is called to add a vote to the system.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_vote(string type,
string description,
string * choices,
int ending)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - Freeform string giving the type of vote. This is typically used
by your completion function so that it can perform different actions for
different types of votes.

%^BOLD%^description%^RESET%^ - The description of the vote as shown to the player.

%^BOLD%^choices%^RESET%^ - An array of vote options eg. ({"Yes", "No" })

%^BOLD%^ending%^RESET%^ - An integer time of when the vote should be terminated.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/voting_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is called to add a vote to the system.

.EP

